summary:
A Phil Lester gif made me google whether or not whales sneeze. And that led me down this weird rabbit hole.
And also I found...
body:
A Phil Lester gif made me google whether or not whales sneeze. And that led me down this weird rabbit hole.

And also I found which kind of snake I would be.

My spirit animal is a Sonoran Coral Snake apparently. “The best it can do is fart”, aka me after a long day and too many tacos.
